   <title>
    詩詞學會登報反駁「馮睎乾」Fb專頁 稱「亂咬亂噴、唯恐香港不亂」
   </title>
   <link>
    https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E6%94%BF%E7%B6%93/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B1%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%E3%80%8Dfb%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81-%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%82%E5%92%AC%E4%BA%82%E5%99%B4%E3%80%81%E5%94%AF%E6%81%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%82%E3%80%8D
